		{
			dependencies: ["7439F90F2ECE4041"]
			description: [
				"&6&oHere, at the absolute edge of existence, the architecture twisting around the barren rock isn't eldritch or alien. Spires of rusted iron and forgotten bookshelves disguise themselves as a dark temple. Amidst this archive stands the Night Warden; a frail, mortal silhouette. He wields a tainted purple scythe, a jagged blade of Void-matter that hums not with ancient mana, but with the cold, rhythmic precision of a machine.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"He traded his humanity for a reaper's shadow. He has no magic of his own, only the stolen echoes of the Void and the logic of a man who refused to be forgotten. Break the shadow.\"&r&r"
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "traveloptics:stellothorn"
				tag: {
					"irons_spellbooks:spell_container": {
