		{
			dependencies: ["79D58811F20E6909"]
			description: [
				"&6&oAs the shadowy exile falls, his tainted purple scythe clattering against the stone, the Miasma dissipates into stardust. His dying whispers speak of a 'fading world'. Yet looking back at the Overworld, arcane magic thrives and the wheels of logic still turn. The fading he feared was only ever his own isolation. The Pact of the Gate holds strong, bridging the ancient divide.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"A world he thought was dying was only ever waiting to be united. The corruption ends here.\"&r&r"
			]
			id: "4701732E94298B2A"
